<item>
            <title>[SOLR-15944] Tagger JSON should use an object, not an array</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-15944</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The SolrTextTagger&apos;s tag structure in JSON looks like this by default:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;tags&quot;:[[
      &quot;startOffset&quot;,6,
      &quot;endOffset&quot;,19,
      &quot;ids&quot;,[&quot;5128581&quot;]]]
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;But really it should be in an object form:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;&quot;tags&quot;:[{
      &quot;startOffset&quot;:6,
      &quot;endOffset&quot;:19,
      &quot;ids&quot;:[&quot;5128581&quot;]}]
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Reported on the dev list by a user: &lt;a href=&quot;https://lists.apache.org/thread/45x8q8x8zjhqbv9n7fyczyq558t2rfcv&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://lists.apache.org/thread/45x8q8x8zjhqbv9n7fyczyq558t2rfcv&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This is easily fixed.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
